/target
# Bulk-ignore models/, then un-ignore the three routelet artifacts the
# shipped binary loads at startup. They are checked in so CI builds the
# .dmg / tarballs with the classifier bundled. Everything else under
# models/ (training artifacts, fp32 backups, setfit experiments) stays out.
/models/**
!/models/routelet/
!/models/routelet/embedder.onnx
!/models/routelet/head.json
!/models/routelet/tokenizer.json
!/models/routelet/MODEL_CARD.md
!/models/routelet/eval_routelet.py
!/models/routelet/confusion_matrix.png
.env
launcher/src-tauri/gen/
*.wav
aegis/evals/results/
node_modules/
